import React, { Fragment } from "react"

import { Canvas } from "react-three-fiber"

const Application = () => {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <Canvas>
        <mesh>
          <boxBufferGeometry 
            attach="geometry"
            args={[2, 2, 2]}
          />
          <meshStandardMaterial
            attach="material"
          />
        </mesh>
      </Canvas>
    </Fragment>
  )
}

export default Application
